	ignore errors.

2003-07-18  Tony Graham  <tonygraham@users.sourceforge.net>

	* dot_emacs: Added commented-out autoloads of `xsl-grep' and
	`xsl-process'.

	* xslide.el: Removed one of two autoloads of
	`reporter-submit-bug-report'.

